snippet.title: Project Amber
snippet.description:
Travelling Europe and the UK in my converted ex-ambulance with my Sprocker Spaniel Pup, Lance.

The 8 month trip around Europe has now come to an end.
It was incredible and got me hooked on Vanlife.
It’s not glamorous like some will have you believe, but it is freeing and addictive way to live life.
But right now My aim is to fix up my van make the changes needed to it for an even more action packed round 2 and get back out there!
Subscribe to follow along. 👍🏻
